Detailed Description

cvmx_l2c_ver_id

L2C_VER_ID = L2C Virtualization ID Error Register

Description: records virtualization IDs associated with HOLEWR/BIGWR/VRTWR/VRTIDRNG/VRTADRNG interrupts.
